*Amanda* je devojka sa velikim srcem. (Amanda is a girl with a big heart.)

*Amanda* je živela u gradu punom nade. (Amanda lived in a city full of hope.)

Ona voli da pročita knjigu koju je *Amanda* napisala. (She likes to read the book that Amanda wrote.)

*Amandi* je bilo potrebno mnogo truda da postigne svoj cilj. (Amanda needed a lot of effort to achieve her goal.)

Istorija o *Amandi* je inspirisala mnoge. (The story of Amanda inspired many.)